body.h1: PBPK model for methacetin based liver function tests (LiMAx and MBT).
body.p:
This model is a physiological-base pharmacokinetic model (PBPK) for the absorption, distribution, metabolism and elimination of methacetin, bicarbonate and paracetamol encoded in SBML format.
The model is applied to the analysis of methacetin based breath tests (MBT) and LiMAx.
body.div: The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort.
This file has been created by Matthias Koenig.
